title: Football preview | Nansemond River at No. 4 Indian River
text:
Tuesday's game Nansemond River at No. 4 Indian River, 7 p.m.
Records: Nansemond River 3-2; Indian River 4-1
Fast fact: This game was postponed from Oct. 1, and moving it to today gives the Warriors and Braves three games in spans of eight and seven days, respectively. Indian River is coming off a devastating 15-14 loss to Oscar Smith on Saturday, and plays at Deep Creek on Friday. Nansemond River lost Thursday to Western Branch and plays at home against Great Bridge on Friday.
Larry Rubama says: Indian River, 26-20.
Jami Frankenberry says: Indian River, 21-13.
